Writing Data in KAFKA server using Pyspark

    spark-submit --packages org.apache.spark:spark-streaming-kafka-0-10_2.12:3.0.1,org.apache.spark:spark-sql-kafka-0-10_2.12:3.0.1 <path>

Writing Data from KAFKA server to console using Pyspark

   spark-submit --packages org.apache.spark:spark-sql-kafka-0-10_2.12:3.2.4,org.apache.spark:spark-streaming-kafka_2.11:1.6.3,io.delta:delta-spark_2.12:3.1.0 --conf "spark.sql.extensions=io.delta.sql.DeltaSparkSessionExtension" --conf "spark.sql.catalog.spark_catalog=org.apache.spark.sql.delta.catalog.DeltaCatalog" <path>
   